<task id="changeoil" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Creating the Glooglob</title>
    <shortdesc>How to create the Glooglob</shortdesc>
    <taskbody>
        <context>the procedure on how what to use to make the Glooglob<p>The most important thing is
                to keep the Glooglob hydrated. If it hardens it has no use.</p></context>
        <steps>
            <stepsection>To create the Glooglob:</stepsection>
            <step>
                <cmd>Take one liter of glue and pour it into a bowl</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>let the glue settle for best results</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Take one package of store bought jelly.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Pour half of the jar into the bowl. .</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Stir the bowl  until fully mixed.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Pour the rest into the bowl and mix.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Let the mix settle.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Once ready, apply water to substance before use.</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
